{
  "id": "608566bb3d9acf001c6f4773",
  "title": "算術の基本定理",
  "created": 1619355335,
  "updated": 1656661948,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "608566bb3d9acf001c6f4773",
      "text": "算術の基本定理",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619355335,
      "updated": 1619355335
    },
    {
      "id": "608569181280f00000054403",
      "text": "[$ \\forall n\\in\\Bbb{N}\\exists!q:\\Bbb{P}\\rightarrow\\Bbb{N}\\cup\\{0\\};n=\\prod_{p\\in\\Bbb{P}}p^{q(p)}]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619355928,
      "updated": 1619356099
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d86d1280f00000824496",
      "text": "   意外とシンプルな論理式で表せた[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619515503,
      "updated": 1619515503
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d7cb1280f0000082448b",
      "text": " 任意の正整数は、1 を除いて、一つまたはそれ以上の[素数]の積として（因子の順番の違いを除いて）ただ一通りに表すことができる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619515341,
      "updated": 1619515341
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d7cd1280f0000082448f",
      "text": "  [素因数分解の一意性]と呼ばれる性質のこと",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619515343,
      "updated": 1619515344
    },
    {
      "id": "62be83d0774b170000b23477",
      "text": " [$ \\exists!]ただ一つ存在",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1656652753,
      "updated": 1656652812
    },
    {
      "id": "62be8885e6003500003e5421",
      "text": "  「ただ一つ存在するヨ(よ)！」で覚えた[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1656653957,
      "updated": 1656654011
    },
    {
      "id": "62be95716eb4060000672e6f",
      "text": "  existのEだと思ってた（理由はよくわからんがひっくり返っている、任意を表す記号もAがひっくり返っている）[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1656657266,
      "updated": 1656657305
    },
    {
      "id": "62bea7b2e60035000031894f",
      "text": "  　存在記号としてEを反転したものを使いだしたのは[ドイツ]の[数学者]、[論理学者]の[ゲルハルト・ゲンツェン]らしいです[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1656661938,
      "updated": 1656661948
    },
    {
      "id": "62bea7b6e600350000318950",
      "text": "   [https://www.nli-research.co.jp/report/detail/id=64337?site=nli 数学記号の由来について（4）－論理記号（∀、∃、∴、∵等）－　|ニッセイ基礎研究所]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1656661942,
      "updated": 1656661942
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d7c01280f00000824485",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619515330,
      "updated": 1619515348
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d7d31280f00000824490",
      "text": "拡張",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619515348,
      "updated": 1619515352
    },
    {
      "id": "6085691a1280f00000054404",
      "text": " 1を全ての素数の0乗の積[$ 1=2^0 3^0 5^0 7^0\\cdots]で表せば、任意の正整数に拡張できる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619355931,
      "updated": 1619356011
    },
    {
      "id": "608570b3e5172d0000b713a2",
      "text": " 　こういう表し方、何とか進数みたいな名前ついてないのかな[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619357875,
      "updated": 1619357910
    },
    {
      "id": "6085f9ac1280f00000073a69",
      "text": " 　 [p進数]がそれかな？[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619392940,
      "updated": 1619392976
    },
    {
      "id": "608632a8e5172d0000f54125",
      "text": " 　  [\" 「p 進数」とは「2進数」や「3進数」の総称に過ぎない]らしいので違いそう[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619407529,
      "updated": 1619407554
    },
    {
      "id": "6086337ce5172d0000f54127",
      "text": " 　  　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/P%E9%80%B2%E6%95%B0 p進数 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619407741,
      "updated": 1619407743
    },
    {
      "id": "608632c3e5172d0000f54126",
      "text": " 　  　それぞれのpごとに考えるものっぽい",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619407555,
      "updated": 1619407590
    },
    {
      "id": "60863520e5172d0000f54128",
      "text": " 　  でも各指数は[p進付値]というらしい",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619408161,
      "updated": 1619408193
    },
    {
      "id": "6086364fe5172d0000f5412a",
      "text": " 　   [$ x=\\operatorname{sgn}(x) \\cdot p_{1}^{e_{1}} p_{2}^{e_{2}} \\cdots p_{n}^{e_{n}} \\quad\\left(x \\in \\mathbb{Q}, \\ e_{i} \\in \\mathbb{Z}\\right)]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619408464,
      "updated": 1619408571
    },
    {
      "id": "6086367ce5172d0000f5412c",
      "text": " 　   [$ e_i]を[$ x]の[$ p_i]進付値という",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619408508,
      "updated": 1619408526
    },
    {
      "id": "60863542e5172d0000f54129",
      "text": " 　  　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/P%E9%80%B2%E4%BB%98%E5%80%A4 p進付値 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619408194,
      "updated": 1619408199
    },
    {
      "id": "6085757803b2100000e7432b",
      "text": "  暗号化に役立ちそう[U.icon]",
      "userId": "5f16f6af405d31002403b210",
      "created": 1619359097,
      "updated": 1619359156
    },
    {
      "id": "6085772c03b2100000e7432c",
      "text": "  　例えば[$ 7,19,3,11 \\cdots ]のように素数の並びを任意に設定すればシンプルかつ高度な暗号になりそう",
      "userId": "5f16f6af405d31002403b210",
      "created": 1619359533,
      "updated": 1619359716
    },
    {
      "id": "608577e303b2100000e7432d",
      "text": "  　　暗号の定番として[アルファベット]をずらす感じ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1619359716,
      "updated": 1656548158
    },
    {
      "id": "608570dbe5172d0000b713a3",
      "text": " 　　1 = 0000...",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619357915,
      "updated": 1619357920
    },
    {
      "id": "608570dfe5172d0000b713a4",
      "text": " 　　2 = 1000...",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619357920,
      "updated": 1619357924
    },
    {
      "id": "608570e4e5172d0000b713a5",
      "text": " 　　3 = 0100...",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619357924,
      "updated": 1619357929
    },
    {
      "id": "608570e9e5172d0000b713a6",
      "text": " 　　4 = 2000...",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619357929,
      "updated": 1619357935
    },
    {
      "id": "608570f7e5172d0000b713a7",
      "text": " 　　5 = 0010...",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619357944,
      "updated": 1619357947
    },
    {
      "id": "608570fbe5172d0000b713a8",
      "text": " 　　6 = 1100...",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619357948,
      "updated": 1619357951
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d7dc1280f00000824491",
      "text": " 符号函数[$ \\rm sgn]を使えば、[$ \\Bbb{Z}\\setminus\\{0\\}]に拡張できる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619515358,
      "updated": 1619515399
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d8051280f00000824492",
      "text": "  [$ \\forall n\\in\\Bbb{Z}\\setminus\\{0\\}\\exists!q:\\Bbb{P}\\rightarrow\\Bbb{N}\\cup\\{0\\};n=\\mathrm{sgn}(n)\\prod_{p\\in\\Bbb{P}}p^{q(p)}]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619515399,
      "updated": 1619515438
    },
    {
      "id": "6085696c1280f00000054406",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619356012,
      "updated": 1619402028
    },
    {
      "id": "60861d371280f0000072cea8",
      "text": "[算術の基本定理#608569181280f00000054403]から直ちに、任意の自然数[$ n]から[p進付値]を作る函数[$ \\mathcal{P}:\\Bbb{N}\\rightarrow(\\Bbb{P}\\rightarrow\\Bbb{N}\\cup\\{0\\})]の存在が導かれる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619402039,
      "updated": 1619515110
    },
    {
      "id": "60861de91280f0000072cea9",
      "text": " [$ \\mathcal{P}(8)(2)=3]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619402217,
      "updated": 1619402232
    },
    {
      "id": "60861dfa1280f0000072ceaa",
      "text": " [$ \\mathcal{P}(8)(3)=0]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619402234,
      "updated": 1619402242
    },
    {
      "id": "60861e021280f0000072ceab",
      "text": " [$ \\mathcal{P}(36)(3)=2]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619402242,
      "updated": 1619402261
    },
    {
      "id": "60861ecd1280f0000072ceac",
      "text": " [算術の基本定理#6085772c03b2100000e7432c]は数列[$ \\mathcal{P}(n)(2),\\mathcal{P}(n)(3),\\mathcal{P}(n)(5),\\mathcal{P}(n)(7),\\cdots]を並べたものとみなせる",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619402445,
      "updated": 1619402497
    },
    {
      "id": "608639f1e5172d0000f5412f",
      "text": " 負の整数も含めて、[$ a = \\operatorname{sgn}(a) \\prod_p p^{v_{p}(a)}], [$ v_{p}: \\mathbb{Z} \\rightarrow \\mathbb{N} \\cup\\{0\\}]と書ける",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619409393,
      "updated": 1619410509
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d9f7e5172d000071c435",
      "text": "  where[$ v_{p}(a):=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{ll} e_{i}, & \\left(\\exists i \\ p = p_{i} \\right. ) \\\\ 0, & \\left(\\forall i \\ p \\neq p_{i} \\right. ) \\end{array}\\right.]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619515895,
      "updated": 1619515897
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d8f9e5172d000071c42f",
      "text": "  \t[$ a=\\operatorname{sgn}(a) \\cdot p_{1}^{e_{1}} p_{2}^{e_{2}} \\cdots p_{n}^{e_{n}} ]とする",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619515641,
      "updated": 1619515902
    },
    {
      "id": "60863bbfe5172d0000f54136",
      "text": " 　[$ v]が[$ \\mathcal{P}]に相当する",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619409855,
      "updated": 1619410513
    },
    {
      "id": "60863cb4e5172d0000f5413b",
      "text": " 　　[$ v:\\mathbb{P} \\rightarrow (\\mathbb{Z} \\rightarrow \\mathbb{N} \\cup \\{0\\})]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619410100,
      "updated": 1619410561
    },
    {
      "id": "60863c28e5172d0000f54137",
      "text": " 　　[$ \\mathbb{P}]が先に来る？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619410192,
      "updated": 1619410513
    },
    {
      "id": "60863c29e5172d0000f54138",
      "text": " 　　　やっぱり素数ごとに考えるという方向性が多いのかな",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619409962,
      "updated": 1619410513
    },
    {
      "id": "60863b5fe5172d0000f54133",
      "text": "  [$ v_p(a)]は[$ \\mathrm{ord}_p(a)]とも書かれる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619409759,
      "updated": 1619409785
    },
    {
      "id": "608640c1e5172d0000f5413f",
      "text": "  https://pc1.math.gakushuin.ac.jp/~shin/html-files/Algebra_Introduction/2013/Exercises/no5.pdf",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619411137,
      "updated": 1619411139
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d6f41280f00000824481",
      "text": "  よく使われる記号があったの[/icons/知らんかった.icon][takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619515126,
      "updated": 1619515149
    },
    {
      "id": "60863dbae5172d0000f5413d",
      "text": " 素数[$ p]と有理数[$ x]に対して[$ v_p(x)]を、[$ p]が[$ x]を有理数上で割り切る最大の指数として定める",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619410362,
      "updated": 1619411124
    },
    {
      "id": "608640cfe5172d0000f54140",
      "text": " 　[$ x = \\frac{a}{b}\\cdot p^n] [$ (a,b,p)]は互いに素、[$ a>0]なる最大の[$ n]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619411152,
      "updated": 1619411241
    },
    {
      "id": "608640b5e5172d0000f5413e",
      "text": " 　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/P%E9%80%B2%E4%BB%98%E5%80%A4 p進付値 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619411125,
      "updated": 1619411145
    },
    {
      "id": "6086453ee5172d0000f54147",
      "text": " 　例: [$ v_2\\left(\\frac{4}{7}\\right) = v_2\\left(2^2 \\cdot \\frac{1}{7}\\right) = 2]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619412287,
      "updated": 1619412450
    },
    {
      "id": "60864597e5172d0000f54148",
      "text": " 　[算術の基本定理#60864151e5172d0000f54142]より、[$ v_p\\left(\\frac{m}{n}\\right) = v_p(m) - v_p(n)]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619412376,
      "updated": 1619412422
    },
    {
      "id": "60861d361280f0000072cea7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619402038,
      "updated": 1619402038
    },
    {
      "id": "60861f2b1280f0000072ceae",
      "text": "[$ 0]をこの定理に含めるのは無理",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619402539,
      "updated": 1619402562
    },
    {
      "id": "60861f421280f0000072ceaf",
      "text": " [$ 0 = 0^l2^m3^n5^o\\cdots\\ (l\\neq 0,\\ m,n,o > 0)]と、指数に任意性が生じてしまう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619402562,
      "updated": 1619402663
    },
    {
      "id": "608638f6e5172d0000f5412d",
      "text": " 0の場合は便宜上すべての指数を無限大とするらしい",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619409143,
      "updated": 1619409219
    },
    {
      "id": "60863d91e5172d0000f5413c",
      "text": "  0はすべての素数で無限回割り切れると考える",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619410321,
      "updated": 1619410336
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d71f1280f00000824482",
      "text": " 　うーん、好きなやり方じゃないなあ[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619515168,
      "updated": 1619515201
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d73f1280f00000824483",
      "text": " 　 折角整数の範囲で閉じていたのに、無限という取り扱い注意なやばいやつが出てきてしまう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619515202,
      "updated": 1619515227
    },
    {
      "id": "6087d7591280f00000824484",
      "text": " 　 以前任意の指数にできることは変わりない",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619515227,
      "updated": 1619515256
    },
    {
      "id": "6087da37e5172d000071c436",
      "text": " 　 ↓の性質を考えるときに（一応）整合性が取れる値ということで[$ \\infty]が選ばれている模様[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619515960,
      "updated": 1619516017
    },
    {
      "id": "6087da60e5172d000071c437",
      "text": " 　  実利があるのかわからんけど",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619516001,
      "updated": 1619516015
    },
    {
      "id": "60861f2a1280f0000072cead",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1619402539,
      "updated": 1619402539
    },
    {
      "id": "60864150e5172d0000f54141",
      "text": "性質",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619411280,
      "updated": 1619411282
    },
    {
      "id": "60864151e5172d0000f54142",
      "text": " [$ v_{p}(m \\cdot n)=v_{p}(m)+v_{p}(n)]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619411282,
      "updated": 1619413388
    },
    {
      "id": "6086426be5172d0000f54146",
      "text": "  [$ \\log]と同じ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619411563,
      "updated": 1619413388
    },
    {
      "id": "6086464fe5172d0000f54149",
      "text": "  [$ \\small\\operatorname{sgn}(mn) \\prod_{p} p^{v_{p}(mn)} = mn = \\operatorname{sgn}(m) \\prod_{p} p^{v_{p}(m)} \\cdot \\operatorname{sgn}(n) \\prod_{p} p^{v_{p}(n)} = \\operatorname{sgn}(mn) \\prod_{p} p^{v_{p}(m) + v_p(n)}]",
      "userId": "5e5b870dd7f3000017a33682",
      "created": 1619412560,
      "updated": 1656553911
    },
    {
      "id": "608647b9e5172d0000f5414a",
      "text": "  素因数分解の一意性より[$ v_{p}(mn) = v_{p}(m) + v_{p}(n)]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619412921,
      "updated": 1619413388
    },
    {
      "id": "60864164e5172d0000f54144",
      "text": " [$ v_{p}(m+n) \\geq \\min \\left\\{v_{p}(m), v_{p}(n)\\right\\}]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619411301,
      "updated": 1619413388
    },
    {
      "id": "608641bee5172d0000f54145",
      "text": "  例: [$ v_2(4+6) = v_2(2 \\cdot (2 + 3)) = 1 \\geq \\min\\{v_2(4), v_2(6)\\} = \\min\\{2,1\\} = 1]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1619411390,
      "updated": 1619413388
    },
    {
